box of birds
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:cheerful, happy, very good; fine, fit, in health, `chirpy' (often as a reply to a greeting)
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: she's a box of birds: she's right, indicating that all is well.
